This library provides the following algorithms for Root finding :

Bisection Method
Secant Method
Newton Raphson Method
Fixed Point Iteration Method
Aitkens Acceleration for the Fixed Point Iteration
Ridders Method

It is a simple implementation and does not take guard for overflows. Run the make file and then try out the testall file. Go through the header file for usage.
